query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(cc t) NoMergeJoin(cc t ci) NoMergeJoin(cc ci n t cct2) NoMergeJoin(cc cct2 ci n t cct1) NoHashJoin(cc cct1 cct2 ci it2 mi_idx n t mi) NoHashJoin(cc cct1 cct2 ci it2 mi mi_idx n t it1) NoMergeJoin(cc cct1 cct2 ci it1 it2 mi mi_idx mk n t k) */ select min(mi.info) AS movie_budget,
min(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes,
min(n.name) AS writer,
min(t.title) AS complete_violent_movie
from complete_cast AS cc
inner join title AS t
on t.id = cc.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2001
inner join cast_info AS ci
on t.id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.note IN ('(writer)',
'(head writer)',
'(written by)',
'(story)',
'(story editor)')
inner join name AS n
on n.id = ci.person_id AND n.gender = 'm'
inner join comp_cast_type AS cct2
on cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind = 'complete+verified'
inner join comp_cast_type AS cct1
on cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct1.kind IN ('complete',
'cast')
inner join movie_info_idx AS mi_idx
on t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
inner join info_type AS it2
on it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'votes'
inner join movie_info AS mi
on t.id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Crime',
'Crime')
inner join info_type AS it1
on it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'genres'
inner join movie_keyword AS mk
on t.id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
inner join keyword AS k
on k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('murder',
'violence',
'blood',
'gore',
'death',
'female-nudity',
'hospital');
